snippet.title: Suika Shapes (Steam) Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now at: store.steampowered.com/app/2686690/Suika_Shapes/

Featuring 22+ shapes, multiple gamemodes, 5 stages, and 7 modifiers that you combine in any way you choose. Climb the global leaderboards, or check your friends' scores, or just play solo and unlock the achievements for 3000 points and clearing every mode!

Online co-op, local co-op, and co-op through steam remote play all playable! (Play online co-op with only one copy of the game through steam remote play)
